#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.str.lstrip.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.str.lstrip"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.lstrip:1
msgid "Remove leading characters."
msgstr "移除前导字符。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.lstrip:3
msgid ""
"Strip whitespaces (including newlines) or a set of specified characters "
"from each string in the Series/Index from left side. Replaces any non-"
"strings in Series with NaNs. Equivalent to :meth:`str.lstrip`."
msgstr ""
"从 Series/Index 中每个字符串的左侧去除空白字符（包括换行符）或指定的一组"
"字符。将 Series 中任何非字符串替换为 NaN。等效于 :meth:`str.lstrip`。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.lstrip
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.lstrip:8
msgid ""
"Specifying the set of characters to be removed. All combinations of this "
"set of characters will be stripped. If None then whitespaces are removed."
msgstr ""
"指定要移除的字符集合。该字符集合的所有组合都将被去除。如果为 None，则移除"
"空白字符。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.lstrip
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.lstrip:17
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.str.strip`"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.lstrip:18
msgid "Remove leading and trailing characters in Series/Index."
msgstr "移除 Series/Index 中的前导和尾随字符。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.lstrip:20
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.str.lstrip`"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.lstrip:21
msgid "Remove leading characters in Series/Index."
msgstr "移除 Series/Index 中的前导字符。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.lstrip:23
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.str.rstrip`"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.lstrip:24
msgid "Remove trailing characters in Series/Index."
msgstr "移除 Series/Index 中的尾随字符。"

